IF ABL:PLAYER:봉사정신 == 0
    SOURCE:11 = 20
ELSEIF ABL:PLAYER:봉사정신 == 1
    SOURCE:11 = 50
ELSEIF ABL:PLAYER:봉사정신 == 2
    SOURCE:11 = 80
ELSEIF ABL:PLAYER:봉사정신 == 3
    SOURCE:11 = 125
ELSEIF ABL:PLAYER:봉사정신 == 4
    SOURCE:11 = 200
ELSE
    SOURCE:11 = 350
ENDIF

;노예가 소야 혹은 파츄리라면 효과 증강
SIF NO:TARGET == 9 || NO:TARGET == 8
    SOURCE:11 += 500

RETURN 1

